00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,720
and your house is kind of out
in the country a little bit

286
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,400
and you have a whole bunch of land.

287
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,990
So you have a whole
bunch of space available

288
00:11:09,990 --> 00:11:11,850
to where if you wanted to
build things, you could.

289
00:11:11,850 --> 00:11:15,360
You could build a bakery,
you could build a store,

290
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,950
you could build whatever you wanted.

291
00:11:16,950 --> 00:11:18,720
You have tons of space, but ultimately,

292
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,820
you have to build it yourself.

293
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:23,010
Now think about moving into a destination

294
00:11:23,010 --> 00:11:24,990
where you're a part of a vibrant village,

295
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:28,020
a community that has all of
these things already in there.

296
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:30,630
You already have a baker,
you already have a grocer,

297
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:32,160
there is a hardware shop.

298
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,990
All of these things exist in this village

299
00:11:33,990 --> 00:11:35,160
and now it's walkable.

300
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:37,740
You can just walk over and
interface with these things

301
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:39,960
without having to go
and build it yourself.

