00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:45,540
and operating in a VMware
environment in AWS.

304
00:11:45,540 --> 00:11:48,030
You're taking the same
house, the same floor plan,

305
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:49,320
everything that you had before

306
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:51,900
and you're able to move
that into a community

307
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:54,360
that now has all of
these other capabilities.

308
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:57,870
So you can take this workload
that you are running in VMware

