00:12:00,060 --> 00:12:02,370
you have RDS that you're
running in your VPC,

311
00:12:02,370 --> 00:12:04,740
you have S3, you have EFS,

312
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:06,690
you have all these
other cloud capabilities

313
00:12:06,690 --> 00:12:09,960
that are now sitting co-resident
in the same environment

314
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,970
with your VMware-based workloads.

