00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:18,630
that's running inside of VMware

318
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,520
and they may move that over to RDS,

319
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:22,700
but the application
itself is still running

320
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:24,900
in VMware on a VM.

