00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:38,760
we want to be the best place in the world

327
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:40,950
for you to run those
VMware-based workloads.

328
00:12:40,950 --> 00:12:42,660
If, when you move that into the cloud,

329
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:45,210
you want to expand and
extend that application

