00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:28,800
I wanna spend a couple of minutes here.

350
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:32,850
When EVS deploys the VCF stack,

351
00:13:32,850 --> 00:13:35,940
we get inputs from you,
and if you've deployed

352
00:13:35,940 --> 00:13:39,930
a Cloud Builder on VCF stack
on premises, you would see

