00:16:44,370 --> 00:16:46,050
Andy talked about scaling.

418
00:16:46,050 --> 00:16:48,570
So if you think about how do
you scale this environment

419
00:16:48,570 --> 00:16:52,740
that we deploy, think of the
EVS stack that we deploy,

420
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:55,350
the environment as a top level construct.

