00:20:47,790 --> 00:20:52,230
What it also means is
traditionally, AWS has always been

508
00:20:52,230 --> 00:20:53,670
a flat layer three network.

509
00:20:53,670 --> 00:20:57,720
We have a VPC, you deploy a
cinder block, you have subnets.

