525
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:37,020
As you think about your EVS environment,

526
00:21:37,020 --> 00:21:39,330
you probably are going
to connect on premises

527
00:21:39,330 --> 00:21:42,360
to talk to a VMware
environment that's there

528
00:21:42,360 --> 00:21:45,840
