00:29:04,410 --> 00:29:07,830
what we do on prem to the cloud

655
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:09,543
and make it more of a hybrid.

656
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,893
Flexible licensing model.

657
00:29:15,030 --> 00:29:16,180
One of the requirements

